title: Bobby’s Girlfriend Caitlin Answers Quarantine Questions + New Artist Kalie Shorr Tests Positive For Coronavirus + Thomas Rhett Quarantined On His 30th Birthday

description:
Bobby’s girlfriend Caitlin answers all of our questions about their quarantine time together. New country artist Artist Kalie Shorr talks to us about testing positive for coronavirus. Plus, Thomas Rhett talks to us about his new song, quarantined life and turning 30 years old this week!
